# SelectAI — Government Internship Selection Platform
# Read this before every single task. No exceptions.

## What this is
An AI-powered internship selection platform for a Government of India organisation.
Two audiences: candidates (public portal) and admins (JWT-protected dashboard).
Full spec lives in: AI_Selection_System_Design.md — read the relevant section before any module.

---

## !! CURRENT MODE: MOCK (Phase 0) !!
- Frontend only — Next.js + Supabase
- All AI responses are MOCKED with realistic hardcoded data
- Resume storage: Supabase Storage bucket "resumes"
- Database: Supabase (3 tables: job_profiles, applications, interview_answers)
- Admin auth: Supabase Auth
- Do NOT build FastAPI backend yet
- Do NOT make real Groq or HuggingFace API calls yet
- Goal: working clickable demo that replicates the full UI workflow end-to-end

